{"id": "art-2703", "label": "Art. 2703", "title": "Art. 2703", "slug": "art-2703", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1706888262\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1103\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1706888262\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 270<sup>3</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_401613175\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1102\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_401613175\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Înc&#259;lcarea prevederilor art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>74</span><span style='color:black'> constituie <span\nclass=SpellE>contraven&#355;ie</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> este <span\nclass=SpellE>sanc&#355;ionat&#259;</span> cu amend&#259; de la 2.500 lei, la\n5.000 lei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_643838371\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1101\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_643838371\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Înc&#259;lcarea prevederilor art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>131 alin. (4)</span><span style='color:black'> constituie\n<span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;ie</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\neste <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;ionat&#259;</span> cu amend&#259; de la 5.000\nlei la 10.000 lei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1245465655\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1100\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1245465655\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>1</sup>)Înc&#259;lcarea prevederilor art. 177 alin.\n(1) lit. a) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ale art. 178 constituie <span\nclass=SpellE>contraven&#355;ie</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> se <span\nclass=SpellE>sanc&#355;ioneaz&#259;</span> cu amend&#259; de la 5.000 lei la\n15.000 lei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2139520655\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1099\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2139520655\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Constatarea <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;iilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> aplicarea <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1)-(2<sup>1</sup>) se realizeaz&#259; de c&#259;tre\norganele cu <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;ii</span> de control ale\nMinisterului <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span> - <span class=SpellE>Agen&#355;ia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>Na&#355;ional&#259;</span> de Administrare Fiscal&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ale <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nsale teritoriale. În procesul-verbal de constatare a <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;iei</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (2<sup>1</sup>) se va consemna faptul c&#259;\nneaducerea la îndeplinire a <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. 177 alin. (1) lit. a) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nla art. 178 atrage dizolvarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în\n<span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> art. 237.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_472454798\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1098\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_472454798\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>1</sup>)Dac&#259; în termen de 30 de zile de la data\naplic&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunii</span> <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;ionale</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (2<sup>1</sup>) reprezentantul persoanei juridice nu <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>-a îndeplinit <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la art. 177 alin. (1) lit. a) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nart. 178, în urma verific&#259;rii efectuate de c&#259;tre organele cu <span\nclass=SpellE>atribu&#355;ii</span> de control ale Ministerului <span\nclass=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span> - <span class=SpellE>Agen&#355;ia</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>Na&#355;ional&#259;</span> de Administrare Fiscal&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;ile</span> sale\nteritoriale, tribunalul/tribunalul specializat va putea <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;a</span>\ndizolvarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> la cererea\nMinisterului <span class=SpellE>Finan&#355;elor</span> - <span class=SpellE>Agen&#355;ia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>Na&#355;ional&#259;</span> de Administrare Fiscal&#259;. <span\nclass=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. 237 alin. (3)-(13) se aplic&#259; în\nmod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_412469891\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1097\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_412469891\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Contraven&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute de prezenta <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> le\nsunt aplicabile prevederile <span class=SpellE>Ordonan&#355;ei</span>\nGuvernului nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>2/2001</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind regimul juridic al <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;iilor</span>,\naprobat&#259; cu modific&#259;ri <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;ri prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>180/2002</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}